<i>noun</i>: 폭압 [포갑], 탄압 [타ː납], 억압 [어갑], 압박 [압빡], 박해 [바캐] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>폭압 [포갑]</dt><br>
<dd>oppression; coercion; repression</dd><br>
<dd>폭력을 써서 억지로 누름.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of putting pressure on someone or a group of people, using violence.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>탄압 [타ː납]</dt><br>
<dd>oppression; pressure; suppression</dd><br>
<dd>힘으로 억지로 눌러 꼼짝 못하게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of forcefully pressing someone or something, making any movement impossible.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>억압 [어갑]</dt><br>
<dd>suppression; oppression</dd><br>
<dd>자유롭게 행동하지 못하도록 권력이나 세력을 이용해 강제로 억누름.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of restraining someone from acting freely by using power or authority.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>압박 [압빡]</dt><br>
<dd>1. pressure</dd><br>
<dd>힘으로 세게 누름.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of pressing something or someone strongly by using physical strength.</dd><br>
<dd>2. pressure; oppression</dd><br>
<dd>기운을 못 펴게 세력 등으로 누름.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of pressing someone by using one's influence, etc., so that he/she is intimidated.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>박해 [바캐]</dt><br>
<dd>persecution; oppression</dd><br>
<dd>힘이나 권력을 가지고 다른 사람을 괴롭히거나 못살게 굴어서 해롭게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of harassing or tormenting and causing harm to another person with one's power or authority.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>